      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system for optimized torque across the power band. Power is delivered via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock. The chassis has been maintained with technical precision, including documented subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension with upgraded bushings to ensure neutral handling and sharp turn-in. This example remains mechanically robust, offering a visceral 8,000 RPM redline experience and linear throttle response that defines the golden era of naturally aspirated performance.",
